Class ByteSequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • bacci.giovanni.deunifier.DeUniFier.seq.ByteSequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequence, Serializable, Comparable<Sequence>

    public class ByteSequence
extends Object
implements Sequence
    Byte implememtation of the Sequence interface. Here Sequence and id are stored as a byte array. Strinngs and byte arrays are ancoded using standard UTF-8 format.
    Author:
    Giovanni Bacci
    See Also:
    String.getBytes(Charset), String.String(byte[], Charset), Serialized Form
